(32, 1, '2014-01-26 10:45:13', '2014-01-26 02:45:13', '<div class="one-second column">\r\nWe are proud of each masterpiece we''ve made. We dedicate 100% of ourselves on each project whatever weight and type it is. We are discovering while growing up. We are grateful to our partners for understanding. We are grateful to any strangers for following up. There were sunlight, as well as pain, but is always full of happiness, which we''ll never gain too much. \r\n</div>\r\n<div class="one-second column">\r\n我们为我们的每一个案例自豪。对每一个项目，无论类型、大小，我们都倾注全部的精力；一路探索，一路成长；感谢伙伴们，知遇理解；感谢同路人，扶持相随；5年的心路历程，有阳光、有汗水，但总充满欢笑，我们收获满满。尊重、信赖、精彩、感动……\r\n</div>\r\n[filterable_portfolio categories="8,9,10,11" number="10"]', 'Work <sub>我们的案例</sub>', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'work', '', '', '2014-01-27 00:14:51', '2014-01-26 16:14:51', '', 0, 'http://hbird/?page_id=32', 0, 'page', '', 0),
